title: Norris loses third to Verstappen in late controversy as Leclerc wins US GP
description: Charles Leclerc impressively won the United States Grand Prix in a surprisingly-dominant one-two for Ferrari as Lando Norris lost a crucial third place to title rival Max Verstappen after being penalised for a late overtake on his F1 title rival.
